title: John Kenneth Galbraith - The Great Crash [40kbps audio]
description:
John Kenneth Galbraith - The Great Crash
Audiobook, circa 1986

This is a (rather low-quality, but entirely intelligible) rip of the book-on-tape (yes, cassette) reading of John Kenneth Galbraith's The Great Crash, an excellent book on the events leading up to the stock market crash of 1929.

This is not my rip, nor is it my torrent. (I got it from mininova.) I'm uploading it for a few reasons:

-While the original torrent is reportedly "in the piratebay system," I've yet to find it via searching. Hopefully this torrent will be found more readily.
-The original torrent was zipped. This one is unzipped, and I added an .sfv file, just for kicks.
-If I lose my hard drive ~and~ my flash drive gets smashed (and I lose my .torrents), I want to be able to get it from piratebay. :P


Remember...

Knowledge > cynicism, any day of the week.
